<item>
            <title>[PIG-400] flatten causes schema naming problems</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-400</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Script:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A = load &apos;data&apos; as (name: chararray, age: chararray, gpa: float);&lt;br/&gt;
B = group A by (name, age);&lt;br/&gt;
C = foreach B generate flatten(group) as res, COUNT(A);&lt;br/&gt;
D = foreach C generate res;&lt;br/&gt;
dump D;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Error:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;java.io.IOException: Invalid alias: res in &lt;/p&gt;
{res::name: chararray,res::age: chararray,long}
