        at org.apache.pig.tools.grunt.Grunt.exec(Grunt.java:64)&lt;br/&gt;
        at org.apache.pig.Main.main(Main.java:302)&lt;br/&gt;
Caused by: org.apache.pig.impl.logicalLayer.parser.ParseException: Invalid alias: res in &lt;/p&gt;
{res::name: chararray,res::age: chararray,long}
